PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of MARILYN MARIE SCOTT, of Humboldt, Saskatchewan, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Farm Credit Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Joan Meyer, who has resigned.
